\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>You may request details of personal information which we hold about you under the Data Protection Act 1998. A small fee will be payable. If you would like a copy of the information held on you please write to Kitchen Appliance Centre, Unit 3 Pentrich Road, Giltbrook Industrial Park, Giltbrook, Nottingham, NG16 2UZ.</p>
